---
title: Out-And-About Orzo Pasta Salad Serves 2 | with olives, tomatoes and feta
description: This light and tasty Greek-inspired pasta salad is perfect for enjoying in the summer sun at beach barbecues, park picnics or anywhere your heart desires!

